  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to develop a structured CBT group intervention for women with
      depression of mild or moderate severity and to pilot a randomized controlled trial to compare
      this intervention with usual care in socially deprived areas in Bristol, incorporating
      qualitative methods to assess acceptability.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
